<div class="px-4 md:px-20 lg:px-40 flex justify-center pt-10">
  <div class="layout-content-container flex flex-col max-w-[960px] flex-1">
    <div class="px-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-2">
      <h2
        class="text-[#111816] text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-[-0.015em]"
      >
        Nilai-Nilai Utama Kami
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#5f8c7d] max-w-lg">
        Kami percaya bahwa bisnis lokal adalah jantung dari komunitas. Inilah
        yang kami pegang teguh.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Values Grid -->
<div class="px-4 md:px-20 lg:px-40 flex justify-center py-10">
  <div class="layout-content-container flex flex-col max-w-[960px] flex-1">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-4">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-1 gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-[#dbe6e3] bg-white p-8 flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow group"
      >
        <div
          class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="size-7 text-accent-500"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-[#111816] text-xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Harga Jujur
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#5f8c7d] text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed">
            Transparansi harga tanpa biaya tersembunyi. Kami berupaya menjaga
            harga tetap terjangkau demi mendukung ekonomi keluarga di sekitar
            kami.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-1 gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-[#dbe6e3] bg-white p-8 flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow group"
      >
        <div
          class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="size-8 text-primary-500"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-[#111816] text-xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Kualitas Terjamin
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#5f8c7d] text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed">
            Setiap barang yang masuk ke rak kami melewati kurasi ketat. Dari
            beras hingga sayuran, kami memastikan hanya yang terbaik untuk dapur
            Anda.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-1 gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-[#dbe6e3] bg-white p-8 flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow group"
      >
        <div
          class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="size-7 text-accent-500"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M15.182 15.182a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-6.364 0M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0ZM9.75 9.75c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75S9 10.164 9 9.75 9.168 9 9.375 9s.375.336.375.75Zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75Zm5.625 0c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75s-.375-.336-.375-.75.168-.75.375-.75.375.336.375.75Zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-[#111816] text-xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Ramah &amp; Bersahabat
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#5f8c7d] text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed">
            Bagi kami, pembeli adalah tamu. Kami melayani dengan hati, siap
            mendengarkan cerita, dan membantu menemukan kebutuhan Anda dengan
            senyuman.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
